    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Assis in improving report writing proficiency."), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Extraction of relevant data for INCLUDE's purpose.")), mdx("p", null, "As I reviewed the reports, I realized the foremost need for institutional and human capacity development of our partners. This focus for the next phase was intensified in the operational plan."), mdx("h2", {
