    <p>{`Local structures, as well as the resources and public services of the chambers of industry and commerce at the district level, have been improved. A particular milestone was the establishment of information and service centres for business start-ups and business promotion at eight selected chambers. With support from these centres, more than 1,500 Nepalese citizens had set up or expanded their own companies by November 2013.`}</p>
